    <h1>Full Color Backgrounds</h1>
    <p>Can be attained by adding class <code>.color-bg</code> to the body tag. As of this writing, this is setup by adding a <code>content_for</code> block to the top of each view where a full color background is necessary. This may be improved somehow -- need to check.</p>
    <p>But the principle remains -- add the aforementioned class to the body tag.</p>
